  "source": {
    "root_place_id": 48852578,
    "universe_id": 32287587,
    "name": "Find the Domos [147]",
    "roblox_url": "https://www.roblox.com/games/48852578",
    "description": "No murdering, no zombies, no building, no tycooning, no roleplaying, just a fun scavenger hunt!\n\nCollect 147 differently assorted Domos, whose theme works as a hint for their hidden location (most of the time).\n\nOld VIP t-shirts still work.\n\nJoin the Fan Group to post your creations of domos, domo ideas, or talk to fellow domo hunters!\nwww.roblox.com/My/Groups.aspx?gid=325808\n\nUnfortunately I don't think I will be updating this game further, but thanks everyone for playing it meant a lot.",
